	"keywords": "Responsive Design, Web Design",
	"description": "For a long time, responsive web design was a trend. Now it&#x27;s simply a reality.\nIf we think of a website, we don&#x27;t really have to say &quot;a responsive website&quot;,\nit&#x27;s just an expected reality.\n\nThis means that when we are putting together a website, it must be built keeping\nin mind how it will look on different screen sizes. With how things are trending\ntoday, there must be a strong emphasis on the mobile experience.\n\nRecently, I launched a comprehensive and detailed course on Scrimba called The\nResp",
